<h1>Eldest Director</h1>

<% directors_asc = Director.where.not({ :dob => nil }).order({ :dob => :asc }) %>

<% eldest_director = directors_asc.first %>

<div>
  The eldest director in our dataset right now is <a href="/directors/<%= eldest_director.id %>"> <%= eldest_director.name %> </a>, 

  born on <%= eldest_director.dob.strftime("%B %d, %Y") %>.
</div>
